Interface AppendUndoModel


  • public interface AppendUndoModel
    Model interface. The AppendUndo model consists of the input string and a stack of the strings appended to the output in reverse order.
    Mathematical Model (abstract value and abstract invariant of this):
     type AppendUndoModel is modeled by
   (input: string of character,
    output: string of string of character)
    Constructor(s) (initial abstract value(s) of this):

   ensures
